title: 578. Top 5 GM-Coach Duos + Year 2 QBs to Watch Out For
itunes:title: 578. Top 5 GM-Coach Duos + Year 2 QBs to Watch Out For
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode. To start off, the guys list early training camp standouts based on what they're seeing and hearing from around the league (1:25). Then, the pair comment on Giants head coach Joe Judge's approach to coaching (11:31). Next, DJ reacts to Bucky's top 5 GM-coach duos (17:11). To wrap up the show, DJ and Bucky discuss Year 2 quarterbacks to watch out for (21:45).
